title: Puppet Agent Status
agents: linux
catalog: app/puppet
license: GPL
distribution: arsoft
description:
 This checks the status of the puppet agent.

perfdata:
 Number of successful and failed services.

item:
  The item {daemon} shows the daemon status.

  The item {config} shows the status of the last config run.

inventory:
  Returns two checks for each machine: {daemon} and {config}
